original_title: Shape Pink Power Flat Abs 5 Ways - AB REHAB
overview: This routine features two circuits, each consisting of five exercises. Smith goes through the circuit once, and in the second round, she and Madison make things a bit more challenging, while Jersey repeats the first circuit. Exercises include crunch with diagonal reach, cross crunch, knee tuck, seated Russian twist, and plank with moving feet.
title: Shape Pink Power Flat Abs 5 Ways - AB REHAB
